{"tid":2184523,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[加大資源]預約爆滿檢測中心周四起增名額　政府稱盡量提供服務","createTime":"2020-09-01T15:03:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-01T15:03:51.000Z","uid":291865,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7e2b2f2c06600d336bed3094ee957276ca2d491a","tid":2184523,"uid":291865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T15:03:51.000Z","msg":"普及社區檢測計劃今日展開，首日有12萬6千人接受檢測。截至晚上8時，累積超過67萬4千人預約登記。<br />\n<br />\n原本已預約爆滿的檢測中心，星期四起會增加名額。今日至少8千人未有預約下接受檢測，政府說，日後會因應實際情況，盡量提供服務。<br />\n<br />\n被問到會否造成人群聚集，有違原意，負責計劃的公務員事務局局長聶德權表示，要「人性化」處理。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1547304-20200901.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1547304-20200901.htm&d=H6IDb39AroI58YjM1eqeYSKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=ef667357\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1547304-20200901.htm&h=0f918eab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1547304-20200901.htm</a>"}]}